text: Strong Boy is a lost 1929 American silent comedy movie directed by John Ford and starring Victor McLaglen, Leatrice Joy, J. Farrell MacDonald, Clyde Cook, Buddy Roosevelt, Tom Wilson, Eulalie Jensen, David Torrence. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1929 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:American silent movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by John Ford
title: Strong Boy
